short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly jump to subreddit by typing 'r' into the omnibar

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You can now quickly jump to a subreddit by typing 'r <tab>' into the omnibar.  Recent subreddits you visited are saved for quicker navigation and autocompletion.

THIS IS A PERSONAL PROJECT AND IS NOT AFFILIATED WITH REDDIT IN ANY WAY.

The source code is available here: https://github.com/chriskonstad/rslash.
